nodes.text: Ren'Salla was a Zabrak female living in the Myyydril Caverns within the Kkowir Forest on the Wookiee planet of Kashyyyk during the Galactic Civil War in 1.5 ABY.

Ren'Salla appeared as a non-player character in the video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online role-playing game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011.
